    About this hotel

    A 3-minute walk from Torre Glries tower, this sleek hotel is 5 km from the Plaa de Catalunya, a central square, and 6 km from lively La Boqueria market.

    Chic rooms offer free Wi-Fi and flat-screens, plus minibars, and tea and coffeemakers. Some include colorful murals, Mediterranean tiles, terraces, pull-down beds and/or whirlpool tubs. Upgraded rooms have porch swings and dining areas. Room service is available.

    Theres a Mediterranean restaurant/bar; a breakfast buffet is offered for a fee. Other amenities include a gym, a sauna and a hammam, plus a rooftop terrace with an outdoor pool and a bar. Bike rentals and parking are available.
